            "id": 6009948,
            "title": "〈和碩股東會〉美國生產基地進到評估尾聲 暗示德州成首選",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>和碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4938:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4938\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4938-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日召開股東會，共同執行長鄭光志表示，目前在美國生產基地的評估已經進到尾聲階段，並透露「與其他同業的選址不會相差太遠」，暗指德州可能為首選。另外，鄭光志也說，電力與人才是最需考量的決策點。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009948%2Fl%2F27f9d9c35d8ba64f68e4268e21e3c361.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">和碩董事長童子賢(中)、共同執行長鄧國彥(左)、共同執行長鄭光志(右)。(鉅亨網記者劉玟妤攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>因應美國關稅政策，和碩在北美的布局除有墨西哥廠外，鄭光志指出，北美生產基地不只有墨西哥，美國廠的評估也進到尾聲，待董事會通過後會對外公告，預計 6 月、7 月公布。至於美國設廠地點，鄭光志則表示「與其他同業的地點接近」，暗指德州可能最後選址地。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鄭光志進一步說明，赴美設廠需考慮的面向非常多，包含土地、人力以及電力。其中，由於 AI 伺服器對於電力及人才的需求非常高，因此電力取得以及專業人才是選址最後的決策關鍵。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鄭光志也補充，針對 AI 伺服器，去年開始進行墨西哥廠的產線規劃，預計今年第三季伺服器產線可以正式量產。此外，因應人力問題，也計畫將自動化導入墨西哥及未來的美國廠區。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
